videos.description: PJ Dozier intercepts a bad pass from Utah and in transition gets it to Nikola Jokic who smashes the two-handed dunk.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Jokic throws down two-handed slam on the break) 2021/01/17 ESHEET

videos.headline: Jokic throws down two-handed slam on the break

videos.description: Jamal Murray works his way to the paint and finds the open lane for the one-handed slam.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Murray is cleared for takeoff) 2021/01/17 ESHEET

videos.headline: Murray is cleared for takeoff

videos.description: Jamal Murray gets fouled as he nails the fadeaway 3-pointer before falling to the ground.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Murray drills the deep contested and-1 triple) 2021/01/17 ESHEET

videos.headline: Murray drills the deep contested and-1 triple

videos.description: Bojan Bogdanovic feeds it down low to Rudy Gobert who slams down the one-handed dunk.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Gobert takes a hit while posterizing Barton) 2021/01/17 ESHEET

videos.headline: Gobert takes a hit while posterizing Barton

videos.description: After some good ball movement from the Jazz, Bojan Bogdanovic gets blocked at the rim and Rudy Gobert comes through and jams it in.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Gobert cleans up the blocked shot with a slam) 2021/01/17 ESHEET

videos.headline: Gobert cleans up the blocked shot with a slam

videos.description: Georges Niang gets a second chance to score and he takes it to the hoop while also drawing the foul.
videos.headline: Niang gets the up-and-under contested bucket

videos.description: Nikola Jokic gets the pass inside to JaMychal Green who outreaches the defender and stuffs it in.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One Play (Jokic, Green connect for the slam) 2021/01/17 ESHEET

videos.headline: Jokic, Green connect for the slam

videos.description: Rudy Gobert hauls in the offensive rebound and sneaks a pass through two defenders as Donovan Mitchell runs through and rattles the rim.
